# WKWebExtension.WindowType

**Enumeration**

Constants used by [doc://com.apple.webkit/documentation/WebKit/WKWebExtensionWindow] to indicate the type of a window.

## Declaration

```swift
enum WindowType
```

## Enumeration Cases

- **WKWebExtension.WindowType.normal**: Indicates a normal window.
- **WKWebExtension.WindowType.popup**: Indicates a pop-up window.

## Initializers

- **init(rawValue:)**

## Enumerations

- **WKWebExtension.WindowState**: Constants used by [doc://com.apple.webkit/documentation/WebKit/WKWebExtensionWindow] to indicate possible states of a window.

## Conforms To

- BitwiseCopyable
- Equatable
- Hashable
- RawRepresentable
- Sendable
- SendableMetatype
